#!/bin/sh
_usplash fini
export PS1='\[\e[1;41m\]\u\[\e[44m\]\W\[\e[45m\]â–‘\[\e[0m\] ' HOME=/root USER=root HOST=$(hostname)
while true; do
  # splash; exec openvt -c1 -sw -- /bin/bash
  # splash; openvt -c1 -sw -- /bin/bash
  case "$1" in
  tmux) tmux -S /run/console;;
  vt)
    openvt -c2 -w  -- /bin/bash &
    openvt -c1 -sw -- /bin/bash ;;
  *) splash; /bin/bash -l;;
esac;done